    "Harvester has a more lightweight database, which can be either consolidated or distributed depending on the deployment model.",
    "Users interact with the PanDA system using client tools through the PanDA server.",
    "Details of PanDA components, database, authentication and authorization mechanism, and client tools are explained in the following sections.",
    "JEDI JEDI (Job Execution and Definition Interface) processes tasks and generates jobs for the PanDA server.",
    "The main functions are as follows:• To receive and parse task specifications, which users submit through the PanDA server."
